14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
16 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
17 This act shall be known and may be cited as the "United States
18 and Oklahoma Flag Display Rights Act of 2025".
19 SECTION 2. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
20 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 155.1 of Title 25, unless there
21 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
22 A. No state or local government entity shall prohibit any
23 person from displaying either the flag of the United States of
24 America or the flag of the State of Oklahoma on property owned by or
